<item>
            <title>[LU-7278] sanity-hsm test_24f: unrecognized tar option</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7278</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for sarah_lw &amp;lt;wei3.liu@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/2693e7fa-6b52-11e5-ae45-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/2693e7fa-6b52-11e5-ae45-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_24f failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;Can not recover the tar contents
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;p&gt;test log&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;tar: unrecognized option &apos;--xattrs&apos;
Try `tar --help&apos; or `tar --usage&apos; for more information.
tar: unrecognized option &apos;--xattrs&apos;
Try `tar --help&apos; or `tar --usage&apos; for more information.
 sanity-hsm test_24f: @@@@@@ FAIL: Can not recover the tar contents 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
                <environment>server: lustre-master/3203 RHEL6.7&lt;br/&gt;
client: SLES11 SP3</environment>
